00:13:59,410 --> 00:14:01,125
Two complex numbers.

358
00:14:01,125 --> 00:14:01,625
Right?

359
00:14:01,625 --> 00:14:04,140
It takes two complex numbers
to specify the state of a bit.

360
00:14:04,140 --> 00:14:08,160
And if we have n qubits, and
