00:15:11,926 --> 00:15:12,749
2 to the n, right?

385
00:15:12,749 --> 00:15:14,540
If I've got n bits that
I want to describe,

386
00:15:14,540 --> 00:15:17,091
it's going to take 2 to
the n complex numbers.

387
00:15:17,091 --> 00:15:18,590
So that's how many
